## Timelessness Rules

**DO:**

- Warm palette over cold/tech
- Editorial confidence over flashy effects
- Subtle motion (scroll reveals, gentle hovers)
- Generous whitespace
- Geometric shapes over organic blobs

**DON'T:**

- Glassmorphism or blur-heavy cards
- Neubrutalism
- 3D transforms or perspective
- Parallax chaos
- Pastel gradients

